<td class="navbox-group" style=";background:#dd9;;">Measurement and <a href="/wiki/Time_standard" title="Time standard">Standards</a></td>
<td style="text-align:left;border-left:2px solid #fdfdfd;width:100%;padding:0px;;;" class="navbox-list navbox-even">
